00:34:11,380 --> 00:34:13,290
Seung Ah ma sem zavolala.

461
00:34:14,950 --> 00:34:17,840
Manažérka, odkiaľ poznáte Baek Seung Hu?

462
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:36,750
Posaď sa.

463
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:39,870
Prečo si ma sem zavolala?

464
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:41,660
Dáš si pivo, však?

465
00:34:57,230 --> 00:34:58,370
Chutí ti?

466
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,080
Čo chceš?

467
00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:04,310
Večná láska.

468
00:35:04,970 --> 00:35:06,310
To je názov toho piva.

469
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:07,850
Pripadá ti to, ako nápoj lásky?

470
00:35:08,940 --> 00:35:10,410
Amber ale.

471
00:35:10,410 --> 00:35:14,280
6.4 percent alkoholu.

472
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:17,640
A čo ešte?

473
00:35:20,180 --> 00:35:22,870
Najlepšie chutí pri teplote 7.5°C.

474
00:35:25,990 --> 00:35:28,210
- Čo robíš?
- Čítam ti zloženie.

475
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:32,660
"Pivo na svadbu."

476
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:34,280
"Večná láska".

477
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:37,870
Toto je pivo na tvoju svadbu

478
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:39,810
